users may have termcap, others - ncurses libs (or both of them), and
readline lib requires one of these term libs, so we first check compiling
with -lreadline -ltermcap, then with -lreadline -ncurses.

Or, 2) how did I get to this. By learning *.m4 autoconf macros and
installing/uninstalling readline (I have both libtermcap and libncurses).
It took me a lot of time, because I am learning autoconf stuff too.

