I have no an opinion here yet.

If you want to do something like this, you can write a Setup Wizard using
FvwmScript, prompting about downloading the latest fvwm-themes (which is
probably not small enough to be included in fvwm itself), then installing
it to the system or user space, and restarting fvwm with the new configs.
I can provide you with all needed shell commands to do this.

> Olivier

