> 
> AddToMenu /home/mikehan MissingSubmenuFunction MakeMissingMenu
> AddToMenu /home/mikehan DynamicPopdownAction DestroyMenu recreate /home/mikehan

This should actually be:

DestroyMenu recreate /home/mikehan
AddToMenu /home/mikehan MissingSubmenuFunction MakeMissingMenu
AddToMenu /home/mikehan DynamicPopdownAction DestroyMenu /home/mikehan

Everything else within your script seems to be correct.

