of sample-95.
- It will be very easy to switch to FvwmTheme and to add a very elementary
theme engine (just for colors and window buttons (not button bindings)). 
The only problem is to found at least 10 "colors palettes". 
Any suggestions ?

Warning: I've written a lot of english ... But I will try to re-read all
this english ...

Olivier

