I've been meaning to report this for awhile now, but it's now become so
annoying that I must!  :)

To demonstrate this clearly, I provide a "simple form".

DestroyModuleConfig SimpleForm.*
*SimpleForm.WarpPointer
*SimpleForm.Line center
*SimpleForm.Text "$Title"
*SimpleForm.Line center
*SimpleForm.Selection simple multiple
*SimpleForm.Choice REST REST off "Restart Form?"
*SimpleForm.Line expand
*SimpleForm.Button quit "END"
*SimpleForm.Command $(REST?Module FvwmForm SimpleForm. Title=SimpleForm
REST=on)
*SimpleForm.Nop

At a console, have fvwm "Read" that form in, thusly....

Read /path/to/SimpleForm.
(Note: the trailing dot "." is important!)

Then invoke the form via a command like....

Module FvwmForm SimpleForm. Title=SimpleForm REST=on

The Choice button does not appear selected on startup.
Is this a bug? Or just not implemented properly?

TIA

Alex

