Me too.  These icons are always buried below a window when I
have to click them :-(

[snip]

> > > I'm also not sure about doing the icon as 1x3  to get the label placed
> > > right.
> > >
> > > Any comments?

[snip]

> > 2) Use a colour set instead of Back/Fore to get rid of this
> >    ugly border around the icon title, 
> 
> Hmm, I  didn't   think the 3d  relief   was ugly,  it  looked  like an
> improvement to me.
> 
> As long as Colorsets  sit in an optional module  they don't  seem like
> core  functionality.  Anyone else think Colorsets  should be moved out
