env variable FVWM_SEARCHPATH which contains only one directory (and
which have to be exported by the user) to add an additional directory 
to search for fvwm. Maybe in this case we have to find an other name.

If this is the case, you may ask for a vote (and no objections) for
adding this feature to your patch?

Olivier


