Ability to check for module uniqueness is good, but should be optional.
Say, using UniqueModule command. All current "event" modules (FvwmAuto,
FvwmBanner, FvwmEvent) are very generic/configurable, i.e. they can be
programmed to execute any arbitrary fvwm function, not only autoraise
windows, or set background images, or play sounds, or all together.

